<h1 class="glitch" data-text="Block'Buster">Block'Buster</h1>
<p><a href="https://asafonov.org/blockbuster" target="_blank">Block'Buster</a> is a simple HTML5 arkanoid-type game. It is written in pure Javascript and works in every modern browser. There is also an <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=org.asafonov.blockbuster" target="_blank">Android application</a>.</p>
<p>Every single design element is thoughtfully created by <a href="https://liworld.online">li</a>
<p>Soure code for <a href="https://github.com/asafonov/blockbuster" target="_blank">browser</a> and <a href="https://github.com/asafonov/blockbuster.apk" target="_blank">Android</a> versions are available on github</p>
